"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61762","Home Office","false","2014-09-30","<p> </p><p>The information requested is shown in the following table. This also includes data up until 30 June for each year.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>","Old Bexley and Sidcup","James Brokenshire",,"2014-09-30T15:00:40.1902103Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61762/answer","Biography information for James Brokenshire","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61762/answer","PQ200528 table.doc","PQ200528 table.doc","Processed passport application services","Processed passport application services","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61762/answer","Old Bexley and Sidcup","James Brokenshire","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61762/answer/previousversion/1835","Biography information for James Brokenshire","1","Home Office","Home Office","2014-06-12","Passports","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, how many (a) standard passport applications, (b) fast-track applications and (c) premium service applications were processed in (i) 1 January 2012 to 31 May 2012, (ii) 1 January 2013 to 31 May 2013 and (iii) 1 January 2014 o 31 May 2014.","false","Biography information for Jessica Morden","Newport East","Jessica Morden","200528"
