"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61802","Cabinet Office","false","2014-06-18","<p>The information requested falls within the responsibility of the UK Statistics Authority. I have asked the Authority to reply.</p><p> </p>","Ruislip, Northwood and Pinner","Mr Nick Hurd",,"2014-06-18T12:15:30.447",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61802/answer","Biography information for Mr Nick Hurd","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61802/answer","PQ 200351.pdf","PQ 200351.pdf","ONS Letter to Member","ONS Letter to Member","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/61802/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2014-06-12","Employment: Kettering","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what the level of unemployment in Kettering constituency  was (a) in May 2010 and (b) is at present; and how many net new jobs have been created in the Kettering economy since May 2010.","false","Biography information for Mr Philip Hollobone","Kettering","Mr Philip Hollobone","200351"
